{
  "id": "69b94133f1a0ed1e667dc82d",
  "title": "現代仮名遣いは情報量を減らす",
  "created": 1773748556,
  "updated": 1773763371,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b94133f1a0ed1e667dc82d",
      "text": "現代仮名遣いは情報量を減らす",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748556,
      "updated": 1773748556
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9414b000000000087ac4a",
      "text": "歴史的仮名遣いと現代仮名遣いを比較すると異なっていたものを統合する場合が多い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748556,
      "updated": 1773748591
    },
    {
      "id": "69b96368000000000087ad8d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773757289,
      "updated": 1773757289
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94173000000000087ac4d",
      "text": "[https://www.bunka.go.jp/kokugo_nihongo/sisaku/joho/joho/kijun/naikaku/gendaikana/index.html 文化庁]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748595,
      "updated": 1773748615
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94156000000000087ac4b",
      "text": "振り仮名は[https://kotobank.jp/ コトバンク]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748566,
      "updated": 1773749700
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94664000000000087acfc",
      "text": "\t*のついた漢字の振り仮名は文化庁の表にもとから載っていた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773749860,
      "updated": 1773749889
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94712000000000087acfd",
      "text": "\tヤ行イに(yi)、ワ行ウに(wu)を補足で載せておく",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773750034,
      "updated": 1773750104
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94a19000000000087acff",
      "text": "\t\tQ. 歴史的仮名遣いでも区別がないヤ行イやワ行ウをどう識別するのか？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773750809,
      "updated": 1773750853
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94a46000000000087ad00",
      "text": "\t\t\tA. ヤ行活用のイ段、ワ行活用のウ段であることからわかる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773750855,
      "updated": 1773750892
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94759000000000087acfe",
      "text": "\tヤ行エに𛀁を入れておく",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773750106,
      "updated": 1773750260
    },
    {
      "id": "69b945b7000000000087acfb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773749687,
      "updated": 1773749687
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94286000000000087acfa",
      "text": "table:a",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748870,
      "updated": 1773748885
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94187000000000087ac4e",
      "text": " 音韻\t現仮名\t歴仮名\t例",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748616,
      "updated": 1773749403
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac50",
      "text": "　イ\tい\tい\t石(いし)　報(むく)い(yi)る　赤(あか)い　意図(いと)　愛(あい)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748807,
      "updated": 1773750397
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac51",
      "text": " 　\t\tゐ\t井戸(ゐど)　居る(ゐる、をる)　参(まゐ)る　胃(ゐ)　権威(けんゐ)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773750542
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac52",
      "text": " 　\t\tひ\t貝(かひ)　合図(あひづ)　費(つひ)やす　思(おも)ひ出(で)　恋(こひ)しさ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773750649
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac53",
      "text": " ウ\tう\tう\t歌(うた)　馬(うま、むま)　浮(う)かぶ　雷雨(らいう)　機運(きうん)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773751040
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac54",
      "text": " 　\t\tふ\t買(か)ふ　吸(す)ふ　争ふ(あらそふ、すまふ)　危(あや)ふい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773751224
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac55",
      "text": " エ\tえ\tえ\t柄(え、がら)　枝(えだ)　心得(こころえ)　見える(み𛀁る)　栄誉(えいよ)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773751344
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac56",
      "text": " 　\t\tゑ\t声(こゑ)　植(う)ゑる　絵(ゑ)　円(ゑん)　知恵(ちゑ)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773751437
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac57",
      "text": " 　\t\tへ\t家(いへ)　前(まへ)　考(かんが)へる　帰る(かへる、かひる)　救(すく)へ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773751545
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac58",
      "text": " 　\tへ\tへ\t西(にし)へ進(すす)む",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773751599
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac59",
      "text": " オ\tお\tお\t奥(おく)　大人(おとな)　起(お)きる　お話(はなし)　雑音(ざつおん)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773751688
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac5a",
      "text": " 　\t\tを\t男(をとこ)　十日(とをか)　踊る(をどる)　青い(あをい)　悪寒(をかん)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773751761
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac5b",
      "text": " 　\t\tほ\t顔(かほ)　氷(こほり)　滞(とどこほ)る　直(なほ)す　大(おほ)きい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773751845
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac5c",
      "text": " 　\t\tふ\t仰(あふ)ぐ　倒(たふ)れる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773751894
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac5d",
      "text": " 　\tを\tを\t花(はな)を見(み)る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773751981
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac5e",
      "text": " カ\tか\tか\t蚊(か)　紙(かみ)　静(しづ)か　家庭(かてい、やには)　休暇(きうか)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773752121
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac5f",
      "text": " 　\t\tくわ\t火事(くゎじ)　歓迎(くゎんげい)　結果(けっくゎ)　生活(せいくゎつ、しゃうくゎつ)　愉快(ゆくゎい)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773752731
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac60",
      "text": " ガ\tが\tが\t石垣(いしがき)　学問(がくもん)　岩石(がんせき)　生涯(しゃうがい)　発芽(はつが)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773752695
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac61",
      "text": " 　\t\tぐわ\t画家(ぐゎか)　外国(ぐゎいこく)　丸薬(ぐゎんやく)　正月(しゃうぐゎつ)　念願(ねんぐゎん)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773752755
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac62",
      "text": " ジ\tじ\tじ\t初(はじ)め　こじあける　字(じ)　自慢(じまん)　術語(じゅつご)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773752691
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac63",
      "text": " 　\t\tぢ\t味　恥ぢる　地面　女性　正直",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773748975
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac64",
      "text": " 　\tぢ\tぢ\t縮む　鼻血　底力　近々　入れ知恵",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773749141
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac65",
      "text": " ズ\tず\tず\t鈴　物好き　知らずに　人数　洪水",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773749318
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac66",
      "text": " 　\t\tづ\t水　珍しい　一つづつ　図画　大豆",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773748978
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac67",
      "text": " 　\tづ\tづ\t鼓　続く　三日月　塩漬け　常々",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773749140
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac68",
      "text": " ワ\tわ\tわ\t輪　泡　声色　弱い　和紙",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773749353
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac69",
      "text": " 　\t\tは\t川　回る　思はず　柔らか　琵*琶*（びは）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773748988
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94192000000000087ac6a",
      "text": " 　\tは\tは\t我は海の子　又は",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748627,
      "updated": 1773749139
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94195000000000087ac6c",
      "text": " ユー\tゆう\tゆう\t勇気　英雄　金融",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748630,
      "updated": 1773749354
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac6d",
      "text": " 　\t\tゆふ\t夕方",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749001
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac6e",
      "text": " 　\t\tいう\t遊戯　郵便　勧誘　所有",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749003
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac6f",
      "text": " 　\t\tいふ\t都邑*（といふ）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749004
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac70",
      "text": " 　\tいう\tいふ\t言ふ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749136
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac71",
      "text": " オー\tおう\tおう\t負うて　応答　欧米",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749356
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac72",
      "text": " 　\t\tあう\t桜花　奥義　中央",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749008
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac73",
      "text": " 　\t\tあふ\t扇　押収　凹凸",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749009
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac74",
      "text": " 　\t\tわう\t弱う　王子　往来　卵黄",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749011
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac75",
      "text": " 　\t\tはう\t買はう　舞はう　怖うございます",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749012
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac76",
      "text": " コー\tこう\tこう\t功績　拘束　公平　気候　振興",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749357
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac77",
      "text": " 　\t\tこふ\t劫*（こふ）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749014
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac78",
      "text": " 　\t\tかう\t咲かう　赤う　かうして　講義　健康",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749016
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac79",
      "text": " 　\t\tかふ\t甲乙　太閤*（たいかふ）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749017
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac7a",
      "text": " 　\t\tくわう\t光線　広大　恐慌　破天荒",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749018
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac7b",
      "text": " ゴー\tごう\tごう\t皇后",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749358
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac7c",
      "text": " 　\t\tごふ\t業　永劫*（えいごふ）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749022
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac7d",
      "text": " 　\t\tがう\t急がう　長う　強引　豪傑　番号",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749023
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac7e",
      "text": " 　\t\tがふ\t合同",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749024
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac7f",
      "text": " 　\t\tぐわう\t轟*音（ぐわうおん）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749025
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac80",
      "text": " ソー\tそう\tそう\t僧　総員　競争　吹奏　放送",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749360
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac81",
      "text": " 　\t\tさう\t話さう　浅う　さうして　草案　体操",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749028
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac82",
      "text": " 　\t\tさふ\t挿話",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749029
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac83",
      "text": " ゾー\tぞう\tぞう\t増加　憎悪　贈与",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749362
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac84",
      "text": " 　\t\tざう\t象　蔵書　製造　内臓　仏像",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749031
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac85",
      "text": " 　\t\tざふ\t雑煮",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749033
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac86",
      "text": " トー\tとう\tとう\t弟　統一　冬至　暴投　北東",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749363
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac87",
      "text": " 　\t\tたう\t峠　勝たう　痛う　刀剣　砂糖",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749034
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac88",
      "text": " 　\t\tたふ\t塔　答弁　出納",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749035
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac89",
      "text": " ドー\tどう\tどう\tどうして　銅　童話　運動　空洞",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749365
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac8a",
      "text": " 　\t\tだう\t堂　道路　葡*萄*（ぶだう）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749039
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac8b",
      "text": " 　\t\tだふ\t問答",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749040
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac8c",
      "text": " ノー\tのう\tのう\t能　農家　濃紺",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749367
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac8d",
      "text": " 　\t\tのふ\t昨日",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749044
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac8e",
      "text": " 　\t\tなう\t死なう　危なうございます　脳　苦悩",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749046
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac8f",
      "text": " 　\t\tなふ\t納入",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749047
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac90",
      "text": " ホー\tほう\tほう\t奉祝　俸給　豊年　霊峰",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749369
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac91",
      "text": " 　\t\tほふ\t法会",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749049
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac92",
      "text": " 　\t\tはう\t葬る　包囲　芳香　解放",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749050
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac93",
      "text": " 　\t\tはふ\tはふり投げる　[はふはふの体]　法律",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773763371
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac94",
      "text": " ボー\tぼう\tぼう\t某　貿易　解剖　無謀",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749370
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac95",
      "text": " 　\t\tぼふ\t正法",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749055
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac96",
      "text": " 　\t\tばう\t遊ばう　飛ばう　紡績　希望　堤防",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749057
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac97",
      "text": " 　\t\tばふ\t貧乏",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749058
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac98",
      "text": " ポー\tぽう\tぽう\t本俸　連峰",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749372
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac99",
      "text": " 　\t\tぽふ\t説法",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749060
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac9a",
      "text": " 　\t\tぱう\t鉄砲　奔放　立方",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749062
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac9b",
      "text": " 　\t\tぱふ\t立法",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749063
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac9c",
      "text": " モー\tもう\tもう\tもう一つ　啓蒙*（けいもう）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749373
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac9d",
      "text": " 　\t\tまう\t申す　休まう　甘う　猛獣　本望",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749064
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac9e",
      "text": " ヨー\tよう\tよう\t見よう　ようございます　用　容易　中庸",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749377
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087ac9f",
      "text": " 　\t\tやう\t八日　早う　様子　洋々　太陽",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749066
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087aca0",
      "text": " 　\t\tえう\t幼年　要領　童謡　日曜",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749068
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087aca1",
      "text": " 　\t\tえふ\t紅葉",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749074
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087aca2",
      "text": " ロー\tろう\tろう\t楼　漏電　披露",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749378
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087aca3",
      "text": " 　\t\tろふ\tかげろふ　ふくろふ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749077
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087aca4",
      "text": " 　\t\tらう\t祈らう　暗う　廊下　労働　明朗",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749078
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a1000000000087aca5",
      "text": " 　\t\tらふ\t候文　蝋*燭*（らふそく）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748641,
      "updated": 1773749080
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a2000000000087aca7",
      "text": " キョー\tきょう\tきよう\t共通　恐怖　興味　吉凶",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748643,
      "updated": 1773749195
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087aca9",
      "text": "　\t\tきやう\t兄弟　鏡台　経文　故郷　熱狂",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749245
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acaa",
      "text": "　\t\tけう\t教育　矯正　絶叫　鉄橋",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749247
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acab",
      "text": "　\t\tけふ\t今日　脅威　協会　海峡",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749248
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acac",
      "text": "　ギョー\tぎょう\tぎよう\t凝集",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749236
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acad",
      "text": "　\t\tぎやう\t仰天　修行　人形",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749249
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acae",
      "text": "　\t\tげう\t今暁",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749251
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acaf",
      "text": "　\t\tげふ\t業務",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749252
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acb0",
      "text": "　ショー\tしょう\tしよう\t昇格　承諾　勝利　自称　訴訟",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749234
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acb1",
      "text": "　\t\tしやう\t詳細　正直　商売　負傷　文章",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749253
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acb2",
      "text": "　\t\tせう\t見ませう　小説　消息　少年　微笑",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749254
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acb3",
      "text": "　\t\tせふ\t交渉",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749256
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acb4",
      "text": "　ジョー\tじょう\tじよう\t冗談　乗馬　過剰",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749257
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acb5",
      "text": "　\t\tじやう\t成就　上手　状態　感情　古城",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749259
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acb6",
      "text": "　\t\tぜう\t饒*舌（ぜうぜつ）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749260
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acb7",
      "text": "　\t\tぢやう\t定石　丈夫　市場　令嬢",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749261
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acb8",
      "text": "　\t\tでう\t箇条",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749262
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acb9",
      "text": "　\t\tでふ\t一帖*（いちでふ）　六畳",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749264
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acba",
      "text": "　\tぢょう\tぢやう\t盆提△灯△（ぼんぢやうちん）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749267
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acbb",
      "text": "　\t\tでう\t一本調子",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749266
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acbc",
      "text": "　チョー\tちょう\tちよう\t徴収　清澄　尊重",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749228
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acbd",
      "text": "　\t\tちやう\t腸　町会　聴取　長短　手帳",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749272
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acbe",
      "text": "　\t\tてう\t調子　朝食　弔電　前兆　野鳥",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749273
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acbf",
      "text": "　\t\tてふ\t蝶*（てふ）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749275
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acc0",
      "text": "　ニョー\tにょう\tによう\t女房",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749226
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acc1",
      "text": "　\t\tねう\t尿",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749277
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acc2",
      "text": "　ヒョー\tひょう\tひよう\t氷山",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749225
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acc3",
      "text": "　\t\tひやう\t拍子　評判　兵糧",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749279
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acc4",
      "text": "　\t\tへう\t表裏　土俵　投票",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749281
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acc5",
      "text": "　ビョー\tびょう\tびやう\t病気　平等",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749224
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acc6",
      "text": "　\t\tべう\t秒読み　描写",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749283
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acc7",
      "text": "　ピョー\tぴょう\tぴよう\t結氷　信憑*性（しんぴようせい）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749223
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acc8",
      "text": "　\t\tぴやう\t論評",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749285
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acc9",
      "text": "　\t\tぺう\t一票　本表",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749288
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acca",
      "text": "　ミョー\tみょう\tみやう\t名代　明日　寿命",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749222
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087accb",
      "text": "　\t\tめう\t妙技",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749289
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087accc",
      "text": "　リョー\tりょう\tりよう\t丘陵",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749221
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087accd",
      "text": "　\t\tりやう\t領土　両方　善良　納涼　分量",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749291
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087acce",
      "text": "　\t\tれう\t寮　料理　官僚　終了",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749292
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941ad000000000087accf",
      "text": "　\t\tれふ\t漁　猟",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748863,
      "updated": 1773749293
    },
    {
      "id": "69b941a2000000000087aca8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748643,
      "updated": 1773748643
    },
    {
      "id": "69b94188000000000087ac4f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773748616,
      "updated": 1773748616
    }
  ]
}